You can use the Auth0 Management API `GET` [/api/v2/refresh-tokens/\{id}](/docs/api/management/v2/refresh-tokens/get-refresh-token) and [/api/v2/sessions/\{id}](/docs/api/management/v2/sessions/get-session) endpoints to retrieve the stored data in either a refresh token or session’s metadata. 

